reviewText:
This is my second favorite in the series! ALL OF THEM ARE LOVELY and a 10 in my book!
Highlights, or the very, very best of the bunch are..
Angela Melini, Wendy Hamilton, Vicky Smith (Anna Nicole Smith), Cheryl Bachman, Samantha Dorman, Corrinna Harney, Tylyn John.

The PLAYMATES included are ~
** CADY CANTRELL
** ANGELA MELINI
** TONYA BEYER
** WENDY HAMILTON
** VICKI SMITH (Anna Nicole Smith/ Playmate of the Year 1993)
** CHERYL BACHMAN
** SUZI SIMPSON
** SAMANTHA DORMAN
** WENDY KAYE
** CORINNA HARNEY (Playmate of the Year 1992)
** TONYA CHRISTENSEN
** TYLYN JOHN
Be sure to ADD this one to the library! WELL WORTH IT! It will dupe over to DVD also!

I only get the pre-1996 videos for their quality and this one has the personality babes like:Samantha Dorman, Angela Melini, Wendy Hamilton, the infamous Vicky Smith ,Cady Cantrell to name a few. Life seems a whole lot better after you watch this! Get it while they last!
